Threads - small mini processes 
threads can be used to perform multitasking in a software
threads are used in gaming - eg(counter strike to perform multitask operations for a user)
threads can also be used in core processors
threads are used in web application for eg any e comm websites to interact with user as well as send request to the server 
threads can be called in java in multiple ways - 
either by implementing the main cthread class.
or by running a interface of thread class. 
by default in every java code we have atleast 1 thread
